EN: He used a slash to join two wooden planks together.
ZH: 3. 斜杠可以增加书柜的稳定性。
EN: Brackets can enhance the stability of the bookshelf.
ZH: 4. 过去，人们常常用斜杠来指示网址。
EN: In the past, people frequently used slashes to indicate web addresses.
