EN: At the construction site, they use brackets to support the erected steel frame.
ZH: 8. 她从储物间拿出了一根金属斜杠，准备用来搭起帐篷。
EN: She took out a metal bracket from the storage room, ready to use it to set up the tent.
ZH: 9. 这本书的封面上有一道红色的斜杠。
EN: There's a red slash on the cover of this book.
